Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"An Underground Maze!\NLuffy vs. the Tram Human!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he fell down below!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this is happening!\NNo {\i1}senpai{\i0}, no life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left his precious straw hat behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Could it be...?!\N--Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I didn't see that coming!\N--I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're alive, Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't care at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Battle Boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you!\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need him... Let me take Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not gonna forgive you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for your act of violence not just against me\Nbut also against the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fell pretty far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are those rails?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't connect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we go back up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I thought this is the \Nheadquarters of your group!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The railcar will soon arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Silver Pirate Alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a tram human who ate the Roll-Roll Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:34.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,AVELON EXPRESS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avelon Express is on its way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is he one of your allies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the passengers who learn about\Nthe underground mineshafts...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have to be gotten rid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}! Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he try to harm me too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna turn the railcar around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! It's coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crest Head! Let's get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay! Help me, Desire!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speeding up! Speeding up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running near the tracks is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not rush - maintain a walking pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next stop: Rain of Bombs! Rain of Bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you use your barrier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of this sticky thing,\NI can't make the gesture!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ball walking on the rails \Nis strictly prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see no track ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There's a fork ahead!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way should we go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to think! Go right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crest Head! Go right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next stop is hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This train is bound for hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! What should we \Ndo at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Avelon, how are Straw Hat \Nand the others doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They fell down to the lowest layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be sure to take them out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big Sis fell...\N--Along with Straw Hat and the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent the other unit to search for Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on me! Desire is one of my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...dear friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barely...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was gonna die this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said "Go right" so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listened to Straw Hat, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warning - downgrade ahead!\NWarning - downgrade ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hold on to the strap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll get here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn this ball...  I can't break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! Bill's creation can't \Nbe broken that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same guy whose underling tried\Nto kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll never harm his friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at the situation you're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A traitor like you has no right to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A traitor? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made a promise to aim for the top together
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but all of a sudden, you said \Nyou wanted to help Straw Hat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I went out to sea with my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what happened to your pirate group?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I once lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...everything that I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this where...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm gonna... die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that there are survivors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the infamous Desire \Nfrom the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The fastest female pirate racer"!\NIt's my honor to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that person anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was betrayed by a guy I trusted and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I lost my friends and my bike,\Nand now I ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How silly I was, to dream \Nof going to the top...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna dominate the Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I need trustworthy friends\Nto accomplish that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have that Battle Boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy to ride but I'm \Nsure you can make full use of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all of us work together,\Nour dream will come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally met someone who shared my ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the people at the \Nfortress trust Bill too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did you come after Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}\Nto please him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and you told me\Nabout the Straw Hats repeatedly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've been working hard\Nfor your friends like we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your praise doesn't make me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bill guy still sounds fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's way cooler than you or Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ouch! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's too hot!\N--S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming off! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the wisdom of Grandma back home, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do! There's nothing \Nthat Grandma doesn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be Bill's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Can you break it?\N--No, we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you guys dropped from up there too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "too"?\NWho are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Mine is a rich mine and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're in its underground mineshafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're former members of the \NSilver Pirate Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, we couldn't please Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who can't bring \Nhim treasures or people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with bounties will all be tossed down here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and forced to mine ore \Nfrom morning till night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible he is to \Nabandon his own friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're his slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! He wouldn't do such \Na thing to his friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't there any way to get out of here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The railroad is the only connection\Nbetween here and up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we use it,\NAvelon will know immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many people have tried until now\Nbut all of them failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this alarm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Limited Express Avelon will soon arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avelon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see one ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please mind the bombs again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Avelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta remove this sticky thing already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Did Bill really tell you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...get rid of me as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avelon started running wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain of Bombs! Rain of Bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It all came off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Barely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\i1}senpai{\i0}! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this drill that was \Nspecially made by Bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stand by for Straw Hat impalement!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It went through! Why isn't he hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you aiming at?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's not that big!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Tram!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm switching over to Hyper Special Express!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Unbelievable! He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now pulling into the garage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait for me! {\i1}Senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by for track...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...change!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Track change!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain in the butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing tracks! Changing tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He took down Avelon that easily....\N--How strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,AVELON EXPRESS
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:21.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TERMINAL STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.17,0:22:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?! I took down Tram!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.55,0:22:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fought in collaboration with \NLuffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} for the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let's get out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avelon! Hey, Avelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.87,0:22:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.25,0:23:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not responding. He must've failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.34,0:23:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Straw Hat and the others make \Nit up here, we'll be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...bury them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:27.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In front of Luffy and the others \Nwho are climbing over themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:29.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to get above ground, the next \Nassassin, Peseta, appears!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:32.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just when the secret weapons \Nof the Smelt-Smelt Fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:34.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,are\Nabout to burn up everything in the underground mineshafts,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.53,0:23:36.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zoro and the others finally arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:40.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro and Peseta's duel, in which \Ntheir pride is at stake, begins!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:41.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.63,0:23:45.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Sword Technique Heats Up! \NLaw and Zoro Finally Appear!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.30,0:23:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:52.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
